# Carta Manifiesto Signature (SAT Requirement)

Under `Settings > Sign Carta Manifiesto`, [sign the letter](https://dashboard.facturapi.io/settings/manifiesto) to comply with the current RMF regulations.

In this step, the issuing RFC's e.firma (FIEL) is used to sign the manifest letter. To complete the signature process, the following is required:

- `.cer` e.signature file

- `.key` e.signature file

- Private key password

Once completed, you will be able to download the Carta Manifiesto files in PDF, XML, or ZIP formats.
